## Workflow

### Step 1: Ingest

1. Set up tooling aliases:
   ```bash
   {{ prefix }}_SKILLS=~/.kiro/skills
   {{ prefix }}_{{ shim }}=${{ prefix }}_SKILLS/home/{{ skill_name }}/scripts/{{ skill_name }}.sh
   {{ prefix }}_TILING=${{ prefix }}_SKILLS/home/tiling/scripts/run-ttm.sh
   {{ prefix }}_EDITOR=${{ prefix }}_SKILLS/home/editor/scripts/run-editor.sh
   {{ prefix }}_ANALYTICS=${{ prefix }}_SKILLS/home/skill-analytics/scripts/add-invocation.sh
   ```
2. Set tiling activity, record invocation, build layout:
   ```bash
   ${{ prefix }}_TILING activity set "{{ skill_name }}({{ target }}): Ingest"
   ${{ prefix }}_ANALYTICS {{ skill_name }} TRIGGER_TYPE:TRIGGER_NAME
   eval "$(${{ prefix }}_TILING layout build)"
   ```
3. Ingest:
   ```bash
   {{ prefix }}_WD=$(${{ prefix }}_{{ shim }} ingest {{ ingest_args }})
   ```
4. If `ingest` fails: NEEDS_CONTEXT.

